title: Python Simplified
description:
Hi everyone! My name is Mariya and I'm a software developer from Vancouver, British Columbia.
I film programming tutorials about Computer Science Concepts, GUI Applications, Machine Learning and Artificial Intelligence, Automation and Web Scraping, Data Science and even Math! 🤓

title: Python Cowboy
description:
#TrapperMike #PythonCowboy @pythoncowboy
 Mike Kimmel, known as Python Cowboy, is one of the leading professional invasive species hunters in Southern Florida. As the owner of Martin County Trapping & Wildlife Rescue, Mike has made it his mission to manage invasive species populations that threaten Florida's native animals. Alongside his team of dedicated dogs, including his skilled companion Otto, Mike takes on the challenge of removing invasive pythons and other species, helping to protect and restore the unique ecosystem of the Everglades.

📘 Get Your Copy of "Otto's Special Mission In The Florida Everglades" https://a.co/d/7Ry3SdX Python Cowboy created a children’s book that follows Otto’s adventure through the Everglades. With themes of courage, teamwork, and conservation, this book is perfect for young readers who love animals and adventure. It’s a fun way to inspire kids to care about wildlife and understand the value of teamwork in protecting our environment.
